1. *Jezivo* sam se uplašio kada sam čuo glasove iz tame. (I was *terrified* when I heard the voices from the darkness.)
2. To što se desilo je bilo *jezivo*. (What happened was *horrifying*.)
3. Ona me *jezivo* nervira svojim stalnim kritikama. (She *terribly* annoys me with her constant criticism.)
4. Vreme je napolju bilo *jezivo* hladno. (The weather outside was *awfully* cold.)
5. Njegov izgled je bio *jeziv* i odbojan. (His appearance was *frightening* and repulsive.)
6. Čitanje ove knjige me čini *jezivo* tužnim. (Reading this book makes me *deeply* sad.)
7. Uzeli su ga kao taoca i mučili ga *jezivo*. (They took him hostage and tortured him *horribly*.)
8. Te noći sam imao *jeziv* san. (That night I had a *terrifying* dream.)
9. Ovo mesto mi izgleda *jezivo* napušteno. (This place looks *eerily* abandoned to me.)
10. *Jezivo* je koliko ljudi žive u siromaštvu. (It's *horrible* how many people live in poverty.)